ote><span style=\"color: red;\">實行合併派位後，部分學校的確出現男女比例失衡現象。</span>數據顯示，較多女生能夠被分派至第一派位組別的學校，而較多男生則被分派至第三派位組別的學校（當時已實施三個派位組別的制度）。[4]<span style=\"color: red;\">這導致很多第一派位組別的男女校變得像女校一樣，男生成為校內的少數分子</span>。<br />\n<br />\n柴田妹說好的平權平等呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個統計幾科學吓"},{"pid":"4a7e9b514b514309d432bd76d23b93a2a7c7c83f","tid":490802,"uid":36324,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T04:40:00.000Z","msg":"對政府嚟講<br />\n其中一個最大嘅問題要有足夠科學證據，證明男女之間有 relevant difference 去 justify 分兩條隊排<br />\n<br />\n否則 EOC v DoE 判決嘅影響會一直維持，如果政府改返分隊又冇證據，幾乎任何未升中嘅女童(同家長)同埋平機會，都肯定有 standing 申請禁制令唔俾政府改，而政府係冇足夠證據下，不可能抗辯成功<br />\n<br />\n換句話講，一日冇足夠有力嘅科學證據，政府做呢樣野都係嘥錢鳩做"},{"pid":"8c36f1e9e7afe884e7e4c093e5fc4b2af7cf510f","tid":490802,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T04:40:04.000Z","msg":"確保少數精英男性可以享有大多數女性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec67fd1b49259eebcaa578df2107f0d1da2c0a8","tid":490802,"uid":35634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T04:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解分別唔公平？ 男同男比，女同女比，有咩問題？ 咁撚鐘意合併，點解唔將男女廁合併一齊用？</blockquote><br />\n你咪戇鳩啦,<br />\n男女廁合併, 我地仲撚洗去</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱啊 出街急屎都唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7092b96921a459d234c25e9d27c19dbf0e2f217e","tid":490802,"uid":81252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T04:43:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解分別唔